## 多分类中不同方法的精度评估
# http://tecdat.cn/r%e8%af%ad%e8%a8%80%e4%b8%ad%e7%9a%84%e5%a4%9a%e7%b1%bb%e5%88%ab%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98%e7%9a%84%e7%bb%a9%e6%95%88%e8%a1%a1%e9%87%8f%ef%bc%9af1-score-%e5%92%8c%e5%b9%bf%e4%b9%89auc/
